sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Gateway
    participant Auth
    participant API
    participant Stream
    participant Data

    User->>Gateway: Login Request
    Gateway->>Auth: OAuth2 Flow
    Auth-->>Gateway: JWT
    Gateway->>API: Authenticated Request
    API->>Data: CRUD Operation
    API->>Stream: Emit Event
    Stream->>Data: Persist Unified Event
